      "description": "## What's Changed\r\n* Adds GPT4o and updates Perplexity models by @clementpoiret in https://github.com/clementpoiret/ai-mentor/pull/4\r\n* Enhance multilingual support by @clementpoiret in https://github.com/clementpoiret/ai-mentor/pull/5\r\n* Better introducer message by @clementpoiret in https://github.com/clementpoiret/ai-mentor/pull/6\r\n\r\n**Nota bene**: Online models, such as `sonar-*-online` from Perplexity may hallucinate in chat mode. This is because of the inclusion of search results into the context of those models. Prefer direct and complete questions when chatting, or switch to a `sonar-*-chat` model (or OpenAI models).\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/clementpoiret/ai-mentor/compare/1.1.1...v1.2.0",
